How To Use This Weekly Template:


1.	Pull in your daily simulation logs for the week.

2.	Fill in the daily snapshots table.

3.	Analyze trends ‚Äî look for patterns in CPU, RAM, disk, network, and errors.

4.	Flag alerts for immediate action and watch points.

5.	Summarize action items and provide simple recommendations for your client.

6.	Keep this document as part of your weekly reporting workflow ‚Äî over time, you‚Äôll see patterns 
	and can provide more valuable insights.

